{
  "stem": "9245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I said, I'm staying with mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said to my-- but I looked at my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I always looked up at her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was older.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Are you-- what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She says, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I said, what about mother?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She didn't answer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I thought, she's going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I went, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we left mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went through the back doors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we came to-- towards the gate, we were going, that-- the gate-- the-- the direction towards the river not in the other direction.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came to a house where the-- the head of the Judenrat lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the-- he was-- he had a command of the German language.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was the liaison.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Obolsky, O-B-O-L-S-K-Y.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- he was a refugee from Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he knew the English language.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was the liaison between the Judenrat and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If ever there was a bribe involved or any difficulties, there were always-- They always demanded something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- he was relaying the information.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father knocked on his window, and he said to him, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obolsky, are you aware of the fact that the ghetto is surrounded, and-- and-- and something is terrible going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, oh, come on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go-- go back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go back to sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll get up in the morning, and I'll-- I'll fix it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll do something about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOB] But my father didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it-- a strange thing-- thing was happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We came to the gate, and there were no guards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they knew that nobody will dare run in that direction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How could they go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The river is there, and there's a bridge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there are an awful lot of German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
